    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一间潮湿的牢房中醒来，这里位于神秘的瀑布塔最深的地下室。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找出路时，你发现自己并不是第一个陷入困境的人。有人留下了足够的线索，或许能帮助你今晚逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场致敬经典冒险解谜游戏的体验，专注于解开各种谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏文本（英文）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>   谜题与装置</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开各种谜题，与阻挡你离开塔楼的奇异机关互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>逃脱的关键</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现并使用各种物品。这些物品将是你逃脱的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ed5b6c6617de5e034d6ada5c6376dfa5.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ed5b6c6617de5e034d6ada5c6376dfa5.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ed5b6c6617de5e034d6ada5c6376dfa5.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>瀑布塔的秘密</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索塔楼，了解其奇怪居民的独特之处，将是你前进的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/1e8825ce83f43ab4246e663b82752b87.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/1e8825ce83f43ab4246e663b82752b87.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/1e8825ce83f43ab4246e663b82752b87.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
